<h2 local-id=3D"a931f5156809" id=3D"id-90-dayplantemplate-Hi,<Employeename>=
!"><img src=3D"https://madisongrand.atlassian.net/wiki/plugins/servlet/conf=
luence/placeholder/error?i18nKey=3Deditor.placeholder.error&amp;locale=3Den=
_GB&amp;version=3D2" title=3D"Cannot invoke &quot;String.indexOf(int)&quot;=
 because &quot;href&quot; is null" class=3D"transform-error" data-encoded-x=
ml=3D"%3Cac%3Aemoticon+ac%3Aname%3D%22wave%22+ac%3Aemoji-shortname%3D%22%3A=
wave%3A%22+ac%3Aemoji-id%3D%221f44b%22+ac%3Alocal-id%3D%223ac65ab201b2%22+a=
c%3Aemoji-fallback%3D%22%F0%9F%91%8B%22+%2F%3E">&nbsp;Hi, !</h2>
<p local-id=3D"83e769cabf7e"></p>
<p local-id=3D"10a052643b0c">Welcome to . We're glad you're here!</p>
<p local-id=3D"1c60346942fc">I've put together this onboarding plan to help=
 you get up to speed in your new role as a on . Feel free to reach out if y=
ou have any questions =F0=9F=99=82<br></p>
<p local-id=3D"86a800358e00">-</p>
<p local-id=3D"19ca7507cbaf"></p>
</div>
</div>
<div class=3D"cell aside" data-type=3D"aside">
<div class=3D"innerCell">
<p local-id=3D"0d9dd9881e71"></p>
<p local-id=3D"96b7d6e6fb07"></p>
<p local-id=3D"962043742b58"></p>
</div>
</div>
</div>
<div class=3D"columnLayout fixed-width" data-layout=3D"fixed-width">
<div class=3D"cell normal" data-type=3D"normal">
<div class=3D"innerCell">
<hr local-id=3D"2ed740952593">
<p local-id=3D"4edf9ea60961"></p>
<div class=3D"confluence-information-macro confluence-information-macro-inf=
ormation">
<span class=3D"aui-icon aui-icon-small aui-iconfont-info confluence-informa=
tion-macro-icon"></span>
<div class=3D"confluence-information-macro-body">
